Author: Marios Trivyzas <matriv@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Feb 22 12:11:23 2024 +0200

    Fix issue with duplicate units for psql style INTERVALs
    
    Disallow duplicate units in the interval strings, as this can be
    ambiguous and also not conforming with PostgreSQL behaviour.
    
    (cherry picked from commit 76cab1d4a51cda3329cf429e1ac6086dcbeb595e)
    
    # Conflicts:
    #       server/src/main/java/io/crate/interval/PGIntervalParser.java

